laboratory_examinations.findings: Negative for Neisseria Gonorrhoeae by PCR.

The uterus measures 9.0 x 3.8 x 5.5 cm, normal in size and shape. The endometrium measures 2 mm and appears normal. A 1.3 x 1.3 x 1.1 cm round slightly hyperechoic structure is seen in the endometrial cavity without vascularity. The right ovary measures 3.2 x 2.4 x 3.3 cm and the left ovary measures 2.6 x 1.9 x 2.7 cm, with normal arterial and venous flow. A small amount of pelvic free fluid is noted.
